      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Mysterious Glow",
        "Client": "Proud Noblewoman",
        "Description": "A great king once bestowed upon my\r\nancestor a shimmering jewel for his\r\ndeeds. But the radiance of that jewel\r\npales in comparison to that of the\r\nCrimson Glow Valstrax. Legend says\r\nthat the beast\u0027s spirit brings you good\r\nluck! On this very hunt, I hope!",
        "Target": "Slay a Crimson Glow Valstrax",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C9clat myst\u00E9rieux",
        "Client": "Noble fi\u00E8re",
        "Description": "L\u0027\u00E9clat d\u0027un Valstrax \u00E9carlate\r\nsurpasse celui d\u0027un joyau\r\nd\u00E9cern\u00E9 par le roi \u00E0 mon\r\nanc\u00EAtre pour ses exploits. La\r\nl\u00E9gende raconte que l\u0027esprit\r\nde ce monstre porte chance.\r\nPour cette chasse, esp\u00E9rons-le !",
